\begin_layout Standard
李代数 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathfrak{sl}(3)$
\end_inset

 有八个生成元，所有生成元都具有零矩阵迹(trace)：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
G_{1}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & 0 & 1\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right), & \qquad G_{2}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 1\\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right), & G_{3}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & -1 & 0\\
1 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right),\\
G_{4}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 1 & 0\\
0 & 0 & -2
\end{array}\right), & \qquad G_{5}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & 0\\
0 & -1 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right), & G_{6}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & 1 & 0\\
1 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right),\\
G_{7}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
1 & 0 & 0
\end{array}\right), & \qquad G_{8}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 1 & 0
\end{array}\right)
